<div class="careers_who_we_are text-center">
	<h2>WHO WE ARE</h2>
	<p class="text-left">Farmer John employees are hard workers who understand the importance of teamwork and togetherness. That's why when you work at Farmer John, you become part of the Farmer John family. And while this family works hard as a team, we always find ways to have fun! From year-round trips to Dodger Stadium to group retreats and endless taste testings, a career with Farmer John offers a world of excitement and more ways than one to bring home the bacon.</p>
